reviewText: I learned a lot of good history behind the Broncos and my husband enjoyed reliving the big moments!
Excellent team history. At my age, it is enjoyable to remember some of those moments. My son doesn't have that history or even as much interest, but he has still enjoyed it!
Not too detailed.  It is missing important information.  The person I bought it for was disappointed.
Great birthday gift for a loving Dallas fan. Very pleased with shipping and receiving
Great gift for a Broncos fan!!

I think Denver Brocos: The Complete History is a better purchase. It covers most of the same things and has the same footage except it doesn't ignore the Plummer years in favor of that 1 season wonder, absolutely terrible NFL QB Tim Tebow.

Seriously, just ignoring Plummer's time in Denver is a damn insult to the man.
For the Bronco fan and must have.
Shipped right away. I didn't get to watch it because it was a gift to someone else but I haven't heard any complains from them.
Son loved it when he opened his birthday present
